WAR MUSEUM chased just off the inside under coaxing from the three-eighths, spun three wide for home and made no impact. MARY KATHERINE chased six then five wide coming under light coaxing midway on the turn, got carried out ten to eleven paths when outside the injured BANDULU QUEEN who was being eased up and guided outwards through the latter portion of the turn to the quarter pole before being able to escape that rival, then was unable to make an impact. VIRTUAL BEAUTY chased four paths off the inside down the backstretch until tucked inside through the turn, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun three wide for home and tired. REIGN OF THUNDER five paths off the inside down the backstretch, tucked three wide through the turn coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, swung five wide for home and made no impact. BANDULU QUEEN chased along the inside down the backstretch, tipped three wide near the three-eighths and suffered an injury bobbling a bit and was placed under a protective hold and guided outside through the latter portion of the turn carrying out MARY KATHERINE to the ten or eleven path when she was marooned to her outside through it all, got eased up through the stretch and was eventually pulled up near the sixteenth pole and subsequently vanned off.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: STERLING SILVER chased two to three wide coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, continued two to three wide for home, closed well to overhaul the leader inside the final seventy yards and was up in the late stages to prevail. TO A T chased six then five wide coming under coaxing at the three-eighths, swung six wide into upper stretch, closed well to secure the place honors in the late going. CHASING CARA hustled from the gate, dueled four then three wide with ASSET PURCHASE to her inside, widened away through the turn as a pair and got set down spinning three wide into upper stretch, took narrow command a furlong out, shook off her main pace rival before being caught inside the final seventy yards to the finish. CUPIDS GIRL chased five then four wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, swung four wide into upper stretch and offered up a mild kick. ASSET PURCHASE dueled from the two path with CHASING CARA to her outside, widened away as a tandem through the turn coming under coaxing near the quarter pole, spun just off the inside into upper stretch, dug in clinging to the front until headed a furlong out, then weakened in the late stages. MASHNEE GIRL chased just off the inside under coaxing from the three-eighths, spun two to three wide into upper stretch, tired. ARGENTINA GIRL coaxed from the start, chased along the inside under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, spun just off the inside for home and tired. AWILLAWAY got bumped at the start by CHAMPAGNE POETRY, chased five to six wide under coaxing from three furlongs out, went six wide into upper stretch and tired. CHAMPAGNE POETRY broke out at the start bumping the aforementioned foe, chased three to four wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, swung five wide into upper stretch and tired.
